{"tid":1551111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記者協會及攝影記者協會聯合聲明　譴責警方濫用武力","createTime":"2019-09-07T23:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T06:53:37.000Z","uid":50457,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e87feac15e7a5e5b9ca82f5af695a8b4c0abe4db","tid":1551111,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:55:42.000Z","msg":"記者協會及攝影記者協會發出聯合聲明，指警方昨晚10時半左右，在旺角始創中心外推進並拘捕行動期間，在全無示威者的情況下，蓄意向現場記者噴發胡椒噴劑，傷及多名前線記者，譴責警方濫用武力及惡意針對記者阻礙採訪，呼籲警方正視前線警員情緒失控及濫權問題。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指出，至少5名攝影記者及3名記者被直接射中，分別來自香港01、法新社、明報及有線新聞，當中兩人更被直接射向臉部。<br />\n<br />\n協會說，在場記者有出示記者證及戴上印有「PRESS」字樣的頭盔，容易識別。而在場警員沒有出示委任證或警員編號，令記者投訴無門。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479416-20190908.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479416-20190908.htm&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprkPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=131ff81b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479416-20190908.htm&h=3423c3f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479416-20190908.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n黑警日日都辣著唔同的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad92d793b3a13f4ef6ef7d42cb6d311307d75eeb","tid":1551111,"uid":33437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:57:05.000Z","msg":"法新社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103f7ffd7e7079395ebc8722c1c14a018e9df147","tid":1551111,"uid":227992,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:58:39.000Z","msg":"香港01本身垃圾，可以唔洗理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb389075823201506412c9f7316ded9a063717a","tid":1551111,"uid":50457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:58:54.000Z","msg":"明報職工協會嚴厲譴責警方無故向記者噴射胡椒噴霧<br />\n<br />\n明報職工協會向警務處處長盧偉聰發公開信，表示得悉警方星期六晚，在太子拘捕示威者的行動中，明報1名文字記者及2名攝影記者在採訪期間，無故被警方噴射胡椒噴霧。工會對警方無故向站在行人路的記者噴射胡椒噴霧，予以嚴厲譴責，嚴正要求警方保障傳媒人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n工會說，事發時，警方在始創中心彌敦道一帶推進，多名記者上前拍攝警員執法過程，其間多名警員阻擋並曾推撞記者，要求記者返回行人路。該報記者按指示走上行人路，其後警方施放胡椒噴霧，該報3名記者被噴中。<br />\n<br />\n工會又說，當時警方噴射胡椒噴霧方向，只有記者，並無任何示威者，而該報記者均佩戴記者證或穿着反光衣。<br />\n<br />\n工會認為，新聞自由是香港重要的核心價值之一，但由6月起的警方行動中，已發生多次記者受傷及被無禮對待事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479409-20190908.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479409-20190908.htm&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprkPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=47852f52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479409-20190908.htm&h=1df346c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479409-20190908.htm</a>"},{"pid":"649315be6b19ce5d62b81317e0bf73c93aa65062","tid":1551111,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:00:13.000Z","msg":"毅進仔唔識英文，無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9998a5e166f3d4e660602294a36bcacaa909f138","tid":1551111,"uid":50457,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"103f7ffd7e7079395ebc8722c1c14a018e9df147","tid":1551111,"uid":227992,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:58:39.000Z","msg":"香港01本身垃圾，可以唔洗理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:00:44.000Z","msg":"唔關事，第四權必須要扞衛，唔關政見事"},{"pid":"f29984f0dfde77ab5dae0ef4d16f8aeca910c0c1","tid":1551111,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"649315be6b19ce5d62b81317e0bf73c93aa65062","tid":1551111,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:00:13.000Z","msg":"毅進仔唔識英文，無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:01:03.000Z","msg":"減佢人工<